{"type": "article", "id": 24006, "title": "展示蔬果的容器", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-17T07:00:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606151438NQxGa1yF4TBmwsu8.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一套储藏蔬果的容器，它将蔬果展示出来同时提醒你该吃蔬菜了。设计师发现买回来的蔬菜常常遗忘在冰箱里或塑料口袋里，就设计了这组容器，分为三种方法保存，浸泡在水里，放在密闭的容器里和站在水里。你甚至还可以浇水，放在一起也组成一个装饰。<a href=\"http://analogueways.com/gront/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061514360XjvAoyhtZEqB64M.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606151437CqwkcvrJIV7gsONu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606151437KxiVP3musAh87T12.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061514373fx6dwq5NjnrR18i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}